CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 22, 2013

[Cite as 05/22/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-0hio-2062.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013-0315. Haselman v. Rittner.

Fulton App. No. F-12-017. On review of order certifying a conflict. It is determined that no conflict exists. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Kennedy, and O’Neill, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and French, JJ., dissent.
